Rating: 3
This recipe is a twice-baked potato in a casserole dish. It is a great idea for a buffet or large number or people instead of restuffing the potatoes. You could add whatever you like in a twice-baked recipe. However, if you boil instead of baking the potatoes as some suggest then it will completely change the taste and purpose of the recipe. If you make it, bake it.

